<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1935-03-21T14:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1935-03-21T14:00:00-05:00" n="248" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d248">
                            <note rend="inline" type="source">862.20/760: Telegram</note>
                            <head><hi rend="italic">The Ambassador in Germany</hi> (<persName type="from"><hi rend="italic">Dodd</hi></persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                                    State</gloss></hi></head>
                            <opener>
                                <dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Berlin</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1935-03-21T20:00:00+01:00">March 21, 1935—8
                                        p.m.</date><lb/>[Received March 21—4 p.m.]</dateline>
                            </opener>
                            <p>52. A curt reply announced in communiqué form was given today to the
                                French Ambassador upon presentation of the French protest,<note n="54" xml:id="d248fn54"><hi rend="italic">Documents on
                                        International Affairs</hi>, 1935 (London, Oxford University
                                    Press, 1936), vol. <hi rend="smallcaps">i</hi>, p. 67.</note> to
                                the effect that the foundation for the protest does not correspond
                                with the facts and it must therefore be rejected by German
                                Government. Unilateral abnegation of the treaty chief point in
                                French as well as Italian note<note n="55" xml:id="d248fn55"><hi rend="italic">Ibid</hi>., p. 68.</note> and it is understood
                                latter answered similarly.</p>
                            <closer><signed><hi rend="smallcaps">Dodd</hi></signed></closer>
                        </div>
                        </body></text></TEI>